# UAT env vars served from Google Secret Manager instead of the base64 blob.
# Empty by default: UAT gets ALL env from the base64 blob (API_ENV_UAT_B64), which
# already carries the corrected Twilio values — nothing to create in Secret Manager.
#
# To move a var to Secret Manager: add its NAME here and create cb-api-uat-<NAME>.
# One NAME per line; `#` comments and blanks ignored.
